# The 2026 ns-2.35 port layer at src/ns-2.35/ is a fourteen-file
# overlay on stock ns-2.35 (see ADR-0024 for the umbrella layout). The
# overlay's style matches the ns-2.35 originals it replaces, NOT ns-3's
# Microsoft/Allman base. Reformatting these files to ns-3 style would
# defeat the byte-for-byte diff discipline against stock ns-2.35 that
# makes the overlay auditable.
#
# The ancestor walkup stops here, not at the project-root .clang-format,
# so both manual clang-format invocations and check-style-clang-format.py
# respect the disable.
---
Language: Cpp
DisableFormat: true
SortIncludes: Never
...
